reviewText: An excellent documentary of the scientific research coupled with eyewitness and Native American Oral Accounts about the kind of seismic history for this region and our need to be prepared.
Very interesting dvd... Oregon and Washington could be in for some tough times.

Excellent documentary movie.  The author has taken information readily available to anyone and compiled a very informational and educational movie that could be shown in schools to those living near Mt. Rainier, Mt Adams, or any fault zone.
